quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Your God is One God; as for those who do not believe in the hereafter, they have faithless hearts and are puffed up with arrogance"
  16,23,Allah surely knows what they conceal and what they reveal; certainly He does not love the arrogant
  16,24,"When they are asked: \"What is it, that your Lord has revealed?\" They say: \"Fictitious stories of the ancients"
  16,25,Let them bear their own burden in full and that of those whom they have misled in their ignorance. Alas! Evil is the responsibility they are taking